Rating: 4
This is your basic Greek roasted chicken that I have been making for years, but w/o the salt. Cook on the grill if at all possible. I baste with sauce during cooking instead of cooking and then placing in the sauce. When you take the chicken off the grill, just squeeze some additional lemon juice on the bird and you'll be happy.

