This chicken was fantastic. It really held the flavour from the marinade. I did make one major modification and it transformed it from great to heavenly!! I substituted the garlic with bottled minced garlic, ginger and chili. It gave the chicken a nice colour and a little bit of heat but not too much!! I made this with 6 skinless chicken legs so I had to cut down the recipe quite abit. It seems to me that it calls for alot of salt. I cut that back. My husband loved this. We make barbequed chicken legs a couple of times per week and these were the best we've had in ages!!

